<ProductLayout {title} heading="Outdoor Eating" {description} {images} {faqs}>
  <div class="text-xl">
    <p>There's nothing better than eating outside when the conditions allow, and a well-built outdoor dining area means you can do it more often. Whether you want a covered structure to shelter from a shower or a simple decked space with shade overhead, we'll build something that makes the most of your garden.</p>

    <p>We design and build outdoor eating areas that are practical, attractive, and suited to the way you use your garden. From intimate corner setups to larger structures for entertaining, every one is handcrafted from quality timber to last for years.</p>

    <p>To talk through your ideas, give us a call on <strong>01228 512303</strong> or use our contact form to arrange a free consultation.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Offer</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list mb-2">
      <li>Covered outdoor dining areas and sheltered seating</li>
      <li>Timber structures designed to suit your garden</li>
      <li>Optional lighting and power provisions for evening use</li>
      <li>Solid timber construction built to weather Cumbrian conditions</li>
      <li>Designed around how you like to entertain outdoors</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ProductLayout>
